I'll run it. I need to know the ontology name used in Ubergraph or wherever this queries. The code uses `get_slim_list_query(ontology)`.
Looking at `get_slim_list_query`:
```python
f"SELECT DISTINCT ?slim ?label ?comment WHERE {{ GRAPH ?ontology {{ ?ontology a owl:Ontology. ?ontology "
f"<http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title> '{ontology}'^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string>. "
```
So I need the exact title string. "Cell Ontology" matches `cl.owl` title usually.
